# 🚀 LIGTAS ULTRA-PERFORMANCE AI IGNORE
# Strictly enforced recursive blocking for maximum AI speed.

# ─── RECURSIVE DEPENDENCY BLOCK ───
**/node_modules/
**/node_modules/**
**/.next/
**/build/
**/.dart_tool/
**/out/

# ─── CLOUD & DB ARTIFCATS ───
.vercel/
.supabase/
.turbo/
.cache/
.npm/

# ─── ENV & SECRETS ───
